::Zardus/DeathStorm/DevilDuer::

Zardus slams into a boulder from Shuko's shot as he recieves the 
transmission from Nemesis. "Excelent," he responds, "We'll solve the 
problems later. The base is under attack, and new units would be 
apreciated."

He jumps backwards over the boulder, using it for cover while 
shooting at Shuko.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
DeathStorm follows Nemesis back towards base.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
DevilDuer rolls to the left, an explosion from Scattershot's charges 
destroying his boulder. He jumps up, firing at Scattershot and then 
at Unitron.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Perndabot slams into a tree, the missile nearly taking out the bottom 
half of his body. He growls, taking out a launcher and firing it at 
Unitron.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Bloodystrike is thrown forward by Unitron's shot into Animbus' claws. 
He groans, slashing his sword desperately at the predacon.
